OL,3,CTeam GB Olympian pays tribute to late
OL,4,Cmum after two bronze wins
OL,6,FAs athlete Sam Reardon watched the
OL,7,Fopening ceremony from his sofa, little
OL,8,Fdid he realise just days later he
OL,9,Fwould not only be competing, but
OL,10,Fwinning medals, as ITV News' Antoine
OL,11,FAllen reports
OL,13,FTeam GB athlete Sam Reardon told ITV
OL,14,FNews "it meant the world" to win two
OL,15,Fbronze medals at the Paris Olympics -
OL,16,Fpaying tribute to his mum who died
OL,17,Fbefore seeing her son achieve their
OL,18,Fshared dream.
