OL,3,CTeam GB Olympian pays tribute to late
OL,4,Cmum after two bronze wins
OL,6,FThe 20-year-old was not originally
OL,7,Fselected to be in Paris, but an injury
OL,8,Fto another member of Team GB meant he
OL,9,Fgot a last minute call to go to the
OL,10,FOlympics, with Reardon going on to win
OL,11,Ftwo bronze medals in the men's and
OL,12,Fmixed 400m relay.
OL,14,F"I was watching the opening ceremony
OL,15,Fin my room at home thinking ah damn, I
OL,16,Fwish I could have been there," he said.
