OL,3,CTeam GB Olympian pays tribute to late
OL,4,Cmum after two bronze wins
OL,6,F"(It went from) it's not happening but
OL,7,FI wish I could have been there, to
OL,8,Fbeing there and running - and coming
OL,9,Faway and winning two bronze medals,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FHowever, Reardon's biggest fan was
OL,13,Fmissing from the crowd to celebrate
OL,14,Fhis special moment.
OL,16,FHis mum died from a brain tumour when
OL,17,Fhe was just 15 years old. She always
OL,18,Fhad unwavering belief her son would
OL,19,Fone day become an Olympian.
