OL,3,CTeam GB Olympian pays tribute to late
OL,4,Cmum after two bronze wins
OL,6,FEach time he stepped onto the podium,
OL,7,Fhe carried a picture of his mum in his
OL,8,Fpocket.
OL,10,F"She's here right on this podium with
OL,11,Fme," he continued.
OL,13,F"I felt that in myself, in my heart
OL,14,Falready, but to have that in physical
OL,15,Fform as well in way, it meant the
OL,16,Fworld.
OL,18,F"I know she would have loved to have
OL,19,Fbeen there and she would be screaming."
