OL,3,CTeam GB Olympian pays tribute to late
OL,4,Cmum after two bronze wins
OL,6,FBy the time of the LA Olympics in
OL,7,F2028, Sam will be 24 years old and he
OL,8,Faims to fulfill one more promise to
OL,9,Fhis mum.
OL,11,F"She always said one day she wanted to
OL,12,Fsee me on top of the podium singing
OL,13,Fthe national anthem," Reardon said.
OL,15,F"She said she'd be balling her eyes
OL,16,Fout. So that's the ultimate aim, its
OL,17,Fto get on top of that and I think with
OL,18,Fthat sort of motivation I can
OL,19,Fdefinitely get there."
